Paper: hep-th/0009153

Date: 2000-09-20

Title: Deforming Einstein's Gravity

Authors: Ali H. Chamseddine (CAMS, AUB)

Comments: 9 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B504 (2001) 33-37

A deformation of Einstein Gravity is constructed based on gauging thenoncommutative ISO(3,1) group using the Seiberg-Witten map. The transformationof the star product under diffeomorphism is given, and the action is determinedto second order in the deformation parameter.